			</l>
		  </lg></div>			
      </div>

      <div type="apparatus">
        <head>Apparatus</head>
        <p>a, l.1. <foreign lang="grc">Μ</foreign> might be
<foreign lang="grc">Α</foreign>.</p>
        <p>There is no indication of how much is missing to either
side in ll. 2 ff.</p>
      </div>

      <div type="translation">
        <head>Translation</head>
        <ab>a. <gap reason="lost" dim="top" extent="1" unit="line"/> <seg cert="low">on the</seg> twentieth
of the month <gap reason="lost" dim="top" extent="1" unit="line"/></ab>
        <ab>b. <gap reason="lost" dim="top" extent="1" unit="line"/> far from enemies,
by the hands of dear friends.</ab>
      </div>

